{"tid":1880481,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[名校系列] 網上資源集中區 - 哈佛耶魯文理商電腦興趣乜都有","createTime":"2020-02-15T00:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:25:47.000Z","uid":141601,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1a06190478a601bb15250bc9dd4ecd4118c54066","tid":1880481,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"[名校系列 ]<br />\n1. 哈佛： <a href=\"https://www.edx.org/school/harvardx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fschool%2Fharvardx&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=e193a60d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/school/harvardx</a><br />\n簡介：個網系由哈佛官方整嘅網上課程，課程大部分免費<br />\n好處：\b真實哈佛上堂錄影，大部分唔洗錢，進度自訂。有聯校課程。<br />\n壞處：自律要求極高，部份服務要俾錢（某d course改assignment，Degree)，唔俾錢無Cert<br />\n推介：<br />\nI. 文科：<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/justice-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Fjustice-2&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=f97c8437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/justice-2</a><br />\n（哲學，正義）<br />\nII. 理科：<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/cs50s-introduction-to-computer-science\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Fcs50s-introduction-to-computer-science&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=716343e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/cs50s-introduction-to-computer-science</a><br />\n（電腦科學，programming)<br />\nIII. 商科： <a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/fintech-ethics-and-risks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Ffintech-ethics-and-risks&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=939d1516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/fintech-ethics-and-risks</a><br />\n（fintech，hku，有中文transcript）<br />\n<br />\n切勿自爆<br />\n<br />\n開錯台重開"},{"pid":"f4351c0ff4df45c7a443ae5eaaed176a44f06431","tid":1880481,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8144905a4b6878a13203e41a3b80d0fb6809944c","tid":1880481,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"裝晒edX, Khan 同iTunes U 但好難搵方向決定讀啲咩開始好<br />\n求推介"},{"pid":"5c221d46cd3d5510eda3ce6f5866c9fb8113360b","tid":1880481,"uid":324732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6da1460a24bf0135f0cd0efbccd7a5e34cbca2","tid":1880481,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T20:31:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1db23ca03697de61931f8a460cf90e3ab4915fb3","tid":1880481,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"[名校系列 ]<br />\n2. <a href=\"https://www.edx.org/school/mitx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fschool%2Fmitx&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=e22bfe2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/school/mitx</a><br />\n簡介：個網系由MIT官方整嘅網上課程，課程大部分免費。<br />\nMIT中文名系麻省理工學院，於QS世界大學排名力壓哈佛劍橋牛津等，成眾名校之首。<br />\n好處：同1一樣。<br />\n壞處：同1一樣。<br />\n推介：<br />\nI. 文科：<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/ap-microeconomics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Fap-microeconomics&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=c92d8719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/ap-microeconomics</a><br />\n（Microecon微觀經濟, Level: Introductory）<br />\nII. 理科： <a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/machine-learning-with-python-from-linear-models-to\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Fmachine-learning-with-python-from-linear-models-to&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b7da5f63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/machine-learning-with-python-from-linear-models-to</a><br />\n（Machine learning 系大勢所趨，不過個course都幾advance 下，Level: Advanced）<br />\nIII. 商科： <a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/fintech-ethics-and-risks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Ffintech-ethics-and-risks&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=939d1516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/fintech-ethics-and-risks</a><br />\n（fintech，hku，有中文transcript）<br />\n<br />\n切勿自爆"},{"pid":"98876d03870051035226afa138433cd349a09754","tid":1880481,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:57:59.000Z","msg":"[名校系列 ]<br />\n心水清嘅巴打會見到商科我放左hku落去，而唔係哈佛MIT ，呢個係我自己個人私心本地大學，所以放左HKU。<br />\n其實edx 一開始真係得哈佛同MIT，後期先越來越多唔同學校課程，有興趣可以自己去以下網頁，搵相關學校同課程。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=801f2e7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/</a><br />\n下面呢條link可以搵相關大學，十分多名校，包括但不限於常春藤大學(IVY LEAGUE)，<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/schools-partners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fschools-partners&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=eb554a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/schools-partners</a><br />\n<br />\n而本地亦有理工大學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/school/hkpolyux\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fschool%2Fhkpolyux&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=f665f248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/school/hkpolyux</a><br />\n興趣班：<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/designing-and-creating-trousers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Fdesigning-and-creating-trousers&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=595157da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/designing-and-creating-trousers</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/course/designing-and-creating-skirts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2Fcourse%2Fdesigning-and-creating-skirts&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=37716dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/course/designing-and-creating-skirts</a><br />\n（對衣物設計有興嘅巴絲可以睇下上面呢兩個course，其中一個係裙嘅設計同製作）<br />\n<br />\n下次會介紹另一個platform。有機會先再返來講edx"},{"pid":"5607bc5d33e3bc03db7e16bcddabc14835a9f835","tid":1880481,"uid":141601,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8144905a4b6878a13203e41a3b80d0fb6809944c","tid":1880481,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"裝晒edX, Khan 同iTunes U 但好難搵方向決定讀啲咩開始好<br />\n求推介"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"我諗大部份人都係無咩方向，我自己通常網上d course，take左十個，最後完成都係得一兩個。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係自己要有動力去學，持之以恆。<br />\n但每人動力都唔同，多數一係搵食，一係興趣。<br />\n<br />\n最好一開始求期揀一個有興趣，短短地，完成到。完成到一個你先有動力去完成第二個。<br />\n個人經驗係take 1－2個完成機率遠遠高於同時take4－5個。<br />\n有時大貪見到幾個有興趣同時reg，結果多數係無一個完成到。<br />\n<br />\n千里之行，始於足下。"},{"pid":"45d9dd2b40f9ca24dc8daec51e488f3f56f2e571","tid":1880481,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"想讀Law"},{"pid":"9f12d89fd25a330b1c1533181de1d4e99213fe2a","tid":1880481,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"d97572acd5bec788a4a66c94738aa6762e8ce01e","tid":1880481,"uid":345578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f11f94b6b1804c71a42812a86341d541c6bc16","tid":1880481,"uid":130540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:40:29.000Z","msg":"<a