kg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coursera.org%2Flearn%2Ffinancial-markets-global%3F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=d5f2f800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coursera.org/learn/financial-markets-global?</a><br />\n (學校：耶魯大學<br />\n   科目：金融市場<br />\n   程度：入門<br />\n   備註：個professor2013年系諾貝爾經濟學獎得主<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.yale.edu/sites/default/files/styles/horizontal_image/public/d6_files/shiller_1.jpg?itok=cf9i_7mj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yale.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fhorizontal_image%2Fpublic%2Fd6_files%2Fshiller_1.jpg%3Fitok%3Dcf9i_7mj&h=e93db9d0&s={SIZE}\" />）<br />\n<br />\n切勿自爆"},{"pid":"6eb32bb2356a8538d1cd53c46dd74f47cfb55380","tid":1880481,"uid":129805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"留名！"}]}